channel.title: Error: Unable to startup listener on 43594 - port already in use?
channel.description:
After I compile and then run my server on my server.bat I get this error. Error: Unable to startup listener on 43594 - port already in use?
But when I get the error everyone on the server can stay on but when they log out they cant log back in or if new people try it wont work.
I use no-ip and I did port forward. Someone HELP please.
